comments: Thompson (CLE) makes marginal contact with Hutchison (CHI) as they both move toward the rebound.
Thompson (CLE) maintains verticality with a legal collapsed forearm as he blocks Hutchison's (CHI) shot attempt.
Dunn (CHI) legally moves alongside Sexton's (CLE) path during his drive.
Osman (CLE) and Markkanen (CHI) make incidental contact with each other as they both move toward the rebound.
Neither team maintains possession of the ball when it is legally batted into the backcourt. Garland (CLE) legally gathers the ball.
Thompson (CLE) establishes himself in Satoransky's (CHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Dunn (CHI) firms up and establishes himself in Garland's (CLE) path where he absorbs the contact.
Thompson (CLE) touches the ball, which has a chance to score, above rim level after it has hit the backboard.
Hutchison (CHI) brushes Thompson's (CLE) arm after the rebound and doesn't affect his ability to maintain control of the ball.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Markkanen (CHI) for contact with Love (CLE) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Markkanen legally defended Love's driving shot attempt and made incidental contact by brushing his body.
LaVine (CHI) shuffles his feet after receiving the inbound pass on the perimeter.
Satoransky (CHI) and Nance Jr. (CLE) engage and separate during the inbound.
Sexton (CLE) jumps from point A to point B into LaVine's (CHI) backside during his driving shot attempt.
Sexton (CLE) is initially in Markkanen's (CHI) path during the off-ball screen. Both players then briefly engage and separate.
Sexton (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position on LaVine (CHI) as LaVine attempts to receive the inbound pass.
Hutchison (CHI) makes marginal contact with Love (CLE) that doesn't knock him off his direct path toward the basket.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Kornet (CHI) throws an errant pass that tips off LaVine's (CHI) fingertips and goes out of bounds.
Hutchison (CHI) firms up to his spot and makes marginal contact with Love (CLE) during his driving shot attempt.
Dunn (CHI) makes incidental contact with Osman (CLE) during the rebound.
Nance Jr. (CLE) commits a take foul on Dunn (CHI).
